headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GTA Online Bonuses: Yellow Swirl Pajamas & Smoking Jacket (Sep 30 - Oct 3)
content: You've unlocked the Yellow Swirl Pajamas and Smoking Jacket just by logging into GTA Online. You can pick up a set for free at any clothing retailers across Los Santos. Perfect for a sophisticated evening of relaxation after a hard day's work, you'll definitely want this dapper lounge wear in your wardrobe.
